duties_responsibilities.duty: Serve as the supervisor and technical lead of 2-4 individuals at the Ellicott City (Baltimore), Maryland office.
Project discipline lead and oversight of 2-4 employees
Independently apply extensive and diversified knowledge of principles and practices in broad areas of assignments and related fields
Develop electrical design documents and drawings
Conceptual and detailed design of low voltage power distribution, lighting, grounding, motor control systems, PLC/PAC, HMI’s process equipment, and instrumentation
Routinely interact with clients, customers, officials, contractors, and others
Lead project meetings and make presentations
Develop electrical drawings including one-line drawings, electrical schematics, electrical equipment layout, hazardous area classification, grounding layout
Meet expectations for attendance and punctuality
